Text: It is a very busy day for the Shadow Garden.
H-Hey! Get out of the way!
Watch out... I'm in a hurry, too.
Everyone seems so busy today... What's going on?
Nothing in particular. We all just have lots to do.
Guess I'm the only one with free time on my hands...

Why, Delta! Did I just hear you say you have free
time? Maybe I can ask you to help me with
something.
And what if I say no...?

A good girl like you wouldn’t say something like that,
would she?
Ha-ruff... Yeah...

The truth is I have my hands full at the moment,
so I'd like you to go do the shopping for dinner.

The list and money are in the basket, so you can
manage this on your own, right?
Awooo! You mean I get to go to the market?!

W-Well, yes. The market is the best place to go
shopping, after all...

I'll do it! Buying a few things is gonna be
easy-peasy!

All of the sudden I'm starting to wonder if asking
you to help was the best idea...!

You're so busy you'd even ask Delta to help... 
That's certainly a first.

Grr! I'm perfectly capable of going to the market and
showing the list to the people at the shops!

Of course you are, and that's why I asked for your
help...

But please, do be careful, okay? Be sure to watch
your money too, since you only have so much.
Don't you worry! Delta is on the job!
Time for my first errand!
Cheap fish! Cheap fish for sale!

Hey there, my good lady! Come take a look! How about
this color and shine! You won't find fresher anywhere
else!
W-Wow...
The market... It's so lively!

I suppose this will do for tonight's dinner. 
Can you wrap it for me?

Of course, ma'am! Thank you very much! Oh, and here's
a little freebie on the house!
A freebie...!

(You can get free stuff when you shop? 
I never knew that!)

Dang... Looks like there's nothin' for it but a
limited-time sale!

The fish peddler starts clanging away with his bell,
making a racket that summons a stampede of
shoppers.
Excuse me! Please get out of the way!
Whoa!

She is so intense that I instinctively step out of
her path.

I can't believe she spooked me! Th-This is crazy...
It's just like a battlefield!

I-I'd better get serious about my shopping too! There
might not be anything left if I don't hurry up.
(That and Lady Alpha is counting on me, too!)
Let's see... I need meat and fish...
Um, I want this!

Ah yes, some pork belly. Let's see here... Wow, look
at all this! You must have quite a large household,
miss.

Household? Well, I'm not sure what you mean, but I do
have lots of people in my family!

I see, I see, so you have a big family! In that case,
I think you need a little extra! Make sure you eat
lots and get big!

Wow, I got a freebie, just like that! I just might be
a genius when it comes to shopping!
Ahaha, hope to see you again!
Thank ye kindly!

You didn't give me a freebie, but thanks anyway! 
Okay, next is eggs, so... Huh?

*sniff, sniff* Something smells so delicious and...
Meaty!

Step right up and get a kebab sandwich seasoned
with our original spices! You won't find a more
mouth-wateringly delicious snack!
*gulp*

(They look so good... I wanna eat one...
I want one, I want one, I want one!)

Oho, do I have a buyer? Just so happens I have some
grilled up and perfect for eating right now!
Grrr...
(I want one...! But, I only have so much money!)
(If I mess up the shopping...)
"Are you telling me you can't even shop right?!"
A-Awoo...

Lady Alpha's so scary when she gets mad... It makes
me sad, but I'm gonna have to give up on my snack...

I want one, but I gotta say no... I'll be in big
trouble if I run out of money...

Ah, that's too bad... I feel for you, but I've got
a business to run here, so I can't just give out
my sandwiches for fr—
Ah, a thief! It's him again! Get back here, you rat!
Dammit! He got me again! Hey! Someone grab that guy!
Wh-What a jerk!

I was a good girl and resisted temptation! And then
he comes along and just snatches one! No way am
I letting that happen!
Grrraaah!!!
U-Um, miss?!
Heh! Everything here is mine for the pickin'!
Taking stuff without paying for it is cheating!
Huh?
Guargh!
Hey! Don't drop it! What a waste!
Aha! Gotcha!

Hey, mister! I clobbered that thief and got your
sandwich back!

Whoa... Thank you! I saw your handiwork all the way
from here! That guy's been causing all of us no end
of trouble—

Say, by way of thanks, you just keep that sandwich
as a reward!
Really?! Yay, lucky me!
*munch, munch* Shopping is the best!

...And that's how I did my first errand just like
you asked!
Hehe, I'm very happy to hear that!

...Well, I see the meat and fish, but where are
the eggs?
A-Awoo... I forgot...

You got so caught up in your kebab that you came
straight home... What a dummy.

Well, you did accomplish the majority of the things
you needed to do, so I suppose that's not too bad
or your debut outing...
I-I'm sorry...
Shopping...isn't easy!
